as a duke!

370
00:21:47,750 --> 00:21:48,590
Exactly.

371
00:21:48,590 --> 00:21:50,070
Give the world an explanation!

372
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:51,070
Duke Zhenbei

373
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:52,880
