531
00:30:06,360 --> 00:30:07,600
You little brat!

532
00:30:07,600 --> 00:30:09,410
Why didn't you let me know
when you returned?

533
00:30:09,510 --> 00:30:11,120
I was so busy.

534
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:12,220
