535
00:30:12,510 --> 00:30:13,510
It's so hot.

536
00:30:13,510 --> 00:30:14,750
Ningyan, you're back!

537
00:30:14,750 --> 00:30:16,310
- Hurry. I'm hungry.
- Sis.

538
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:19,030
Lingyue, come here.

539
00:30:19,060 --> 00:30:20,990
There are a few dishes left.
