00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:17,960
What? Wait.

566
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:19,200
Niece-in-law?

567
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:20,750
How come I didn't know?

568
00:31:20,990 --> 00:31:22,880
It was from Lin'an.

569
00:31:22,880 --> 00:31:24,750
Lin'an is the best.

570
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:27,440
She buys me different yogurts
every day.

571
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:28,750
It's so delicious!

572
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:32,600
Oh, it's Lin'an.

573
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:34,470
While you were away,

574
00:31:34,470 --> 00:31:37,550
Princess Lin'an would send gifts to us
from time to time.

575
00:31:38,030 --> 00:31:39,230
Princess Lin'an gave Father

576
00:31:39,230 --> 00:31:41,600
the golden saber on him yesterday.

577
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:44,840
He loves it.

578
00:31:44,840 --> 00:31:47,160
Last night, he was holding it
while sleeping.

579
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:48,840
He didn't even hold me.

580
00:31:52,210 --> 00:31:54,470
Speaking of Princess Lin'an,
she'd send people every day

581
00:31:54,470 --> 00:31:56,160
to ask when you'd return.

582
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:57,330
Why hasn't anyone come today?

583
00:31:57,360 --> 00:31:58,200
Yes.

584
00:31:59,030 --> 00:32:00,640
Lin'an must be hiding.

585
00:32:00,790 --> 00:32:01,630
Come out.

586
00:32:01,990 --> 00:32:02,930
