587
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:07,360
Sir, your dish is ready.

588
00:32:07,360 --> 00:32:08,200
Enjoy.

589
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:21,120
Plain noodles again.

590
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:23,070
Can't you give me something else?

591
00:32:24,600 --> 00:32:25,990
I pay for your food and drinks.

592
00:32:25,990 --> 00:32:27,400
How can you still complain?

593
00:32:36,070 --> 00:32:37,200
It's not good.

594
00:32:44,750 --> 00:32:45,680
Let me tell you.

595
00:32:46,450 --> 00:32:48,880
If it weren't for Xu Qi'an
repeatedly telling me

596
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:51,310
to safely bring you back to the capital,

597
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:55,200
I'd throw you into the bandit's den
and let you fend for yourself.

598
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:56,710
Anyway, we're entering the city.

599
00:32:57,840 --> 00:32:58,680
After that,

600
00:32:58,680 --> 00:33:00,270
I'll make sure to repay you.

601
00:33:09,750 --> 00:33:10,640
Your Highness,

602
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:12,070
