603
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:13,540
If Father won't meet with me,

604
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:15,440
I'll kneel here until dawn.

605
00:33:21,310 --> 00:33:22,150
Lin'an.

606
00:33:29,030 --> 00:33:29,990
The ground is cold.

607
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:31,400
Come back with me.

608
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,240
Be good.

609
00:33:33,470 --> 00:33:34,310
Mother,

610
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,550
you've taught me since I was little

611
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:38,330
that a gentleman doesn't harm others

612
00:33:38,410 --> 00:33:39,230
or deceive himself.

613
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,680
Although I am not talented,

614
00:33:42,270 --> 00:33:44,070
I always remember this.

615
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:47,790
Uncle's massacre has caused uproar

616
00:33:48,120 --> 00:33:49,790
in the city today.

617
00:33:50,310 --> 00:33:51,710
The officials tried to advise,

618
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:53,710
yet Father avoided them.

619
00:33:54,840 --> 00:33:55,990
As his daughter,

620
00:33:56,990 --> 00:33:58,550
I cannot sit idly by.

621
00:33:58,550 --> 00:33:59,400
Shut up.

622
00:34:05,310 --> 00:34:06,150
Lin'an,

623
00:34:06,470 --> 00:34:08,470
go back to your Shaoyin Palace

624
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:11,120
or return to your residence outside.

625
00:34:11,230 --> 00:34:12,400
Just don't ask about this

626
00:34:12,400 --> 00:34:13,790
or intervene in this.

627
00:34:13,790 --> 00:34:14,630
Be good.

628
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:18,400
Take the princess away.

629
00:34:19,030 --> 00:34:19,870
Mother.

630
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:20,920
The princess...

631
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:23,720
The princess is concerned
about His Majesty's health,

632
00:34:23,990 --> 00:34:25,670
- so she knelt here to pray.
- Let's go.

633
00:34:25,700 --> 00:34:27,220
Now, her knees hurt too much to stand.

634
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:27,830
Hurry.

635
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:29,320
Help her back to the Palace to rest.

636
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,960
Something serious happened in Chuzhou.

637
00:34:36,240 --> 00:34:37,880
Today, the officials caused uproar.

638
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:39,720
Everyone's talking about it.

639
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:42,440
What happened?

640
00:34:44,280 --> 00:34:45,590
What's so serious?

641
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:48,510
You're a woman.

642
00:34:48,510 --> 00:34:50,110
Why are you asking so many questions?

643
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:53,670
The Dafeng actually has such a beast.

644
00:34:53,720 --> 00:34:55,240
Let's go inside to play.

645
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:56,880
No wonder.

646
00:34:57,670 --> 00:34:59,990
