649
00:35:04,670 --> 00:35:05,590
Nor will he let him

650
00:35:05,990 --> 00:35:07,550
be remembered

651
00:35:07,550 --> 00:35:08,650
as the Dafeng's Protector.

652
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:14,200
Ningyan,

653
00:35:15,190 --> 00:35:16,840
