690
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:51,440
If our guess is right,

691
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:52,840
within three days,

692
00:36:52,990 --> 00:36:53,920
he'll definitely move.

693
00:36:57,150 --> 00:36:58,760
But for now, I'm in a lowly position,

694
00:36:59,070 --> 00:37:00,240
unable to attend court.

695
00:37:01,110 --> 00:37:02,990
Though I can help from the outside,

696
00:37:03,880 --> 00:37:05,510
the real battlefield

697
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,320
should still be left to Lord Wei,

698
00:37:07,720 --> 00:37:08,720
