avenging the people,

706
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,240
pursuing the culprit,

707
00:37:31,240 --> 00:37:32,840
and killing the Mighty Bone.

708
00:37:33,590 --> 00:37:35,030
The thought of this

709
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:37,160
has made my hair

710
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:39,140
