711
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:41,320
Why?

712
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:43,840
Why was it that mysterious man?

713
00:37:43,990 --> 00:37:45,150
Why?

714
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:48,030
The Supervisor held me back!

715
00:37:53,720 --> 00:37:54,670
However,

716
00:37:55,590 --> 00:37:57,590
it wasn't Xu Ningyan

717
00:37:57,670 --> 00:37:59,360
who did those heroic acts after all.

718
00:37:59,720 --> 00:38:02,030
I feel much better.

719
00:38:02,190 --> 00:38:03,070
That kid

720
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:04,110
took my chance away.

721
00:38:04,110 --> 00:38:04,960
How hateful.

722
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:06,760
He must've watched

723
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:09,920
